  "title": "Exeventyre",
  "description": "Exeventyre is a magic RPG mod that adds crystal sorcery to Minecraft!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Exeventyre is a magic RPG mod that adds crystal sorcery to Minecraft!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/736/264/exeventyre_logo_q.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><b>Development of this mod was freezed but you can check my other mods. I made some big ones!</b></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Subscribe on mod's platforms:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/TpP4vAMDgb\">Discord Server</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@unknownraccooneternaltales4940\">YouTube</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a title=\"Telegramm channel\" href=\"https://t.me/eternal_tales_news\">Telegram channel</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://eternaltales.wiki.gg/wiki/Eternal_Tales_Wiki\">Wiki</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://vk.com/eternal_tales\">VK (Russian)&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Some of mod content:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Crystal Caves!</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">New biome where you can find crystals, crystwood and cryslate for crafts.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/736/259/2023-09-30_12.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"644\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Arcanaeum Ore</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">It's the main crafting element in the mod. It drops Arcanaeum Pile that can be crafted into Arcanaeum Dust.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/736/260/2023-09-30_12.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"644\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Brass</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">New metal for crafting. Brass Ingot can be obtained when you smelt Brass Scrap that crafts from Raw Iron, Raw Gold and Raw Copper.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/736/262/2023-06-06_18.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"581\" /></p>",
